results.name: Next-to-last term in n-th row of A080504.
comment: If n is odd, a(n) = n-1. If n is even, n-1 <= a(n) <= 3n/2-1. For even n up to 100, a(n) = 3n/2-1 unless n = 2 or 24; are there other exceptions? - _Dean Hickerson_, Mar 21 2003
results.author: _Dean Hickerson_, Mar 21 2003
